#### 任务列表 (Card 封装)

```css
/* 任务列表 - 清晰的任务清单感 */
.task-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
}

.task-card {
  background: rgb(var(--card));
  border: 1px solid rgb(var(--border));
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 16px 20px;              /* 增加 Padding */

  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 12px;

  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.task-card:hover {
  border-color: rgb(var(--muted));
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
}

.task-card.completed {
  opacity: 0.6;
}

.task-checkbox {
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  border: 2px solid rgb(var(--border));
  border-radius: 4px;
  cursor: pointer;
  flex-shrink: 0;

  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;

  transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.task-checkbox:hover {
  border-color: rgb(var(--primary));
}

.task-checkbox.checked {
  background: rgb(var(--primary));
  border-color: rgb(var(--primary));
}

.task-checkbox.checked::after {
  content: '✓';
  color: rgb(var(--card));
  font-size: 12px;
}

.task-content {
  flex: 1;
}

.task-title {
  font-size: 0.9375rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: rgb(var(--foreground));
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.task-card.completed .task-title {
  text-decoration: line-through;
  color: rgb(var(--muted));
}

.task-meta {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  color: rgb(var(--muted));
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
}

.task-tag {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 2px 8px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  font-size: 0.6875rem;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.task-tag.perma-p { background: rgba(138, 154, 91, 0.15); color: rgb(var(--perma-p)); }
.task-tag.perma-e { background: rgba(102, 123, 153, 0.15); color: rgb(var(--perma-e)); }
.task-tag.perma-r { background: rgba(194, 123, 103, 0.15); color: rgb(var(--perma-r)); }
.task-tag.perma-m { background: rgba(204, 180, 100, 0.15); color: rgb(var(--perma-m)); }
.task-tag.perma-a { background: rgba(120, 109, 140, 0.15); color: rgb(var(--perma-a)); }
```

